###

### Crear sede secundaria
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/branches HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "code": "SEDE-02",
    "repsCode": "05001002",
    "name": "Sede Norte",
    "countryId": 1,
    "departmentId": 5,
    "municipalityId": 1,
    "address": "Carrera 80 # 32-15",
    "phone": "6044446666",
    "email": "sede.norte@mednova.com",
    "isPrincipal": false
}

###

### Obtener sede por ID
GET http://localhost:{{port}}/api/branches/1 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar sedes (sin búsqueda)
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/branches/list HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "page": 0,
    "rows": 10,
    "search": "",
    "order_by": "s.nombre",
    "order": "ASC"
}

###

### Listar sedes (con búsqueda)
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/branches/list HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "page": 0,
    "rows": 10,
    "search": "principal",
    "order_by": "s.nombre",
    "order": "ASC"
}

###

### Actualizar sede
PUT http://localhost:{{port}}/api/branches/1 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Sede Principal Medellín Actualizada",
    "repsCode": "05001001",
    "countryId": 1,
    "departmentId": 5,
    "municipalityId": 1,
    "address": "Calle 50 # 40-25",
    "phone": "6044445556",
    "email": "sede.principal.nueva@mednova.com",
    "isPrincipal": true
}

###

### Marcar otra sede como principal (desmarca la anterior)
PUT http://localhost:{{port}}/api/branches/2 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Sede Norte",
    "repsCode": "05001002",
    "countryId": 1,
    "departmentId": 5,
    "municipalityId": 1,
    "address": "Carrera 80 # 32-15",
    "phone": "6044446666",
    "email": "sede.norte@mednova.com",
    "isPrincipal": true
}

###

### Activar / Inactivar sede (toggle)
PATCH http://localhost:{{port}}/api/branches/1/toggle-active HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

